CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 28, 1958, pg. A7 reads: "Luncheon Committee For Guild - Helping to make the Saturday luncheon at the Press Club a success were these young matrons of the Urban League Guild. Left to right: Kitty Irvis, Dorothea Mason, Alfreta Calloway, Gladys Haines and Lenora Rainey.  Toki Schalk Johnson, president-emeritus of the Pittsburgh Urban League Guild, made the arrangements for the Press Club. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Urban League Guild members, from left: Kitty Irvis, Dorothea Mason, Alfreta Calloway, Gladys Haines, and Lenora Rainey posed in Press Club during luncheon
